{"profile":{"awsPrograms":[{"joinedAt":2026.0,"programName":"USER_GROUP_LEADER"},{"category":"Community Hero","joinedAt":2019.0,"memberStatus":"ACTIVE","programName":"HERO"}],"basicInfo":{"alias":"margaretvaltierra","avatar":"https://avatars.builderprofile.aws.dev/2xnMGooSlHhZGPwyYMZuYXSOiTd.webp","bio":"I bring hands-on expertise in AWS, cloud migrations, and stakeholder communications. I’ve led Agile and DevOps transformations for large and small teams. I am proud to organize the Chicago AWS user group and AWS Community Day Midwest, a user-run conference for over 400 attendees. I can easily translate ambiguous requirements into actionable milestones, align stakeholders across disciplines, and deliver measurable impact. I’ve also presented at AWS re:Invent, the Chicago AWS Summit, and community events—demonstrating my ability to communicate complex technical concepts with clarity and enthusiasm.\n\nAWS Community Day | Midwest Founder and Organizer \nAWS Community Day | Midwest is an annual one-day, technical conference run for the user community, by the AWS user community.  The event has grown from grassroots meetups to a full-scale conference, rotating through Chicago, Columbus, Milwaukee, and now Indy. This work reflects my commitment to building inclusive, high-impact spaces where cloud professionals can connect, learn, and grow. Join us: https://www.midwestcommunityday.com\n\nChicago AWS User Group leader\nSince 2013 I've been connecting the AWS community in Chicago via events and programs. The Chicago AWS Tech community continues to grow and evolve! Join us: https://www.meetup.com/aws-chicago ","builderProfileId":"79b7a9b2-ea97-4839-b5c7-108f810a768b","createdOn":1.711740551168E12,"headline":"AWS Community Hero | Chicago AWS user group leader","isStaff":false,"name":"margaret valtierra"},"location":{"displayLocation":{"countryRegion":"US","stateProvince":"IL"}},"profileStatus":"ACTIVE","socials":{"devto":"https://dev.to/margaretvaltie","github":"https://github.com/margaretvaltie","linkedIn":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/margaretvaltierra","personal":"https://www.margaretmvaltierra.com/"}}}